data.description: Charming single-level property in Denver is the one you've been waiting for! The spacious great room welcomes you with its airy ambiance, emphasized by the tile flooring and neutral color palette that offers a canvas for your personal decor. Discover the fabulous kitchen featuring wood cabinetry adorned with crown moulding, a pantry, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, and a center island including a breakfast bar, perfect for quick meals or morning coffees. Primary bedroom boasts a private bathroom with dual sinks and a generously sized walk-in closet, providing substantial space for wardrobe and storage. You will find a basement with a convenient bonus room ideal for a home theater, gym, or a play area. The impressive backyard showcases manicured green grass and a cozy ramada for outdoor dining or relaxation, making it an excellent space for hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings! What are you waiting for? Create new memories in this fantastic home! Downtown Views from the lower patio/sitting area.
